block content
  .container
    header.header.mt-5.pt-5
      .row
        .col-md-12
          h1= title
          p.header__lead Some description about the #{title}
            |. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit,
            | sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.
            |Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris
            |nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.
    section#house-prices
      article.header.mt-2.pt-5
        .row
          .col-md-4
            h2.header__h1 House Prices
            p House prices in the ROI are expressed in the first chart 
              |as Residential Price Index (RPI). For the NI figures in the second 
              |chart, the House Price Index (HPI) is used

          .col-md-4
            .row
              #rpi-chart
          .col-md-4
            .row
              #hpi-chart

    section#tourism
      article.header.mt-2.pt-5
        .row
          .col-md-4
            h2.header__h1 Tourism
            p The chart shows the total numbers of overnight stays for DCSDC and 
              |NI, broken into the proportions of stays eminating from a variety of origins.
              |The figures are for 2016.

          .col-md-8
            .row
              #tourism-chart-1

    section#employment-rates
      article.header.mt-2.pt-5
        .row
          .col-md-4
            h2.header__h1 Employment Rates
            p The chart shows 
              |
              |

          .col-md-8
            .row
              #employment-chart-1

    section#employment-sectors
      article.header.mt-2.pt-5
        .row
          .col-md-4
            h2.header__h1 Employment By Sector
            p The chart shows 
              |
